@baseUrl = http://localhost:1508
@userId = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
@userIdNotFound = 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
@subjectId = math-101
@activityId = 33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333
@studentId = student-001

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 0) HEALTH / OPENAPI
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### 0.1 Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

### 0.2 OpenAPI JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/api-docs

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### A) POINTS
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### A1. POST points/events - valido
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/points/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actionEvent": "TASK_COMPLETED",
  "completionDate": "2026-05-17T10:00:00",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-17T23:59:00",
  "activityId": "{{activityId}}",
  "userActivityHistory": [
    {
      "actionEvent": "SUBJECT_PROGRESS",
      "completionDate": "2026-05-16T10:00:00"
    }
  ]
}

### A2. GET points - usuario existente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/points

### A3. GET points - usuario inexistente (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userIdNotFound}}/points

### A4. POST points/events - payload invalido (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/points/events
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### A5. POST points/events - duplicado (pointsUpdated=false)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/points/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actionEvent": "TASK_COMPLETED",
  "completionDate": "2026-05-17T10:00:00",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-17T23:59:00",
  "activityId": "{{activityId}}",
  "userActivityHistory": [
    {
      "actionEvent": "TASK_COMPLETED",
      "completionDate": "2026-05-17T10:00:00",
      "activityId": "{{activityId}}"
    }
  ]
}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### B) ACHIEVEMENTS
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### B1. POST achievements/unlock - valido (PERFECT_SCORE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/achievements/unlock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "achievementEvent": "PERFECT_SCORE",
  "userProgressData": [
    {
      "activityType": "EXAM",
      "completionDate": "2026-05-17T10:00:00",
      "score": 100
    }
  ]
}

### B2. POST achievements/unlock - duplicado (achievementUnlocked=false)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/achievements/unlock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "achievementEvent": "PERFECT_SCORE",
  "userProgressData": [
    {
      "activityType": "EXAM",
      "completionDate": "2026-05-17T10:00:00",
      "score": 100
    }
  ]
}

### B3. GET achievements - usuario existente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/achievements

### B4. GET achievements - usuario inexistente (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userIdNotFound}}/achievements

### B5. POST achievements/unlock - payload invalido (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/achievements/unlock
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### C) SUBJECT PROGRESS
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### C1. POST subjects/progress - valido
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/subjects/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjects": [
    {
      "subjectId": "{{subjectId}}",
      "subjectName": "Mathematics",
      "completedTasks": [
        { "taskId": "t1", "taskName": "Homework 1", "xpValue": 10 },
        { "taskId": "t2", "taskName": "Quiz 1", "xpValue": 10 }
      ],
      "totalTasks": 4,
      "academicPerformance": 90.0
    }
  ]
}

### C2. GET subjects/progress - usuario existente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/subjects/progress

### C3. GET subjects/{subjectId}/progress - existente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/subjects/{{subjectId}}/progress

### C4. GET subjects/progress - usuario sin snapshots (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userIdNotFound}}/subjects/progress

### C5. GET subjects/{subjectId}/progress - inexistente (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/subjects/subject-does-not-exist/progress

### C6. POST subjects/progress - lista vacia (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/subjects/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjects": []
}

### C7. POST subjects/progress - subjectId faltante (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/subjects/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjects": [
    {
      "subjectName": "Physics",
      "completedTasks": [],
      "academicPerformance": 70.0
    }
  ]
}

### C8. POST subjects/progress/sync - valido con X-Student-Id
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/subjects/progress/sync
X-Student-Id: {{studentId}}

### C9. POST subjects/progress/sync - sin header (usa userId como fallback)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/subjects/progress/sync

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### D) AIB-35 GAMIFICATION PROGRESS
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### D1. GET progress - perfil de gamificacion academica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/gamification/{{userId}}/progress
